    <description>
        <p>
            Thakir Prayer Times is a desktop application to calculate prayer times for algeria cities:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Accurate Prayer time calculator based on your current location;</li>
            <li>Hijri date;</li>
            <li>With Azan/Adhan: visual and audio notifications/calls for prayer;</li>
            <li>Quibla direction from the sun and magnetic north;</li>
            <li>Enable/Disable Alert before Adhan;</li>
            <li>Enable/Disable Silent mode after Adhan (during Prayer);</li>
            <li>-Arabic GUI.</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
    <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.hafmed.Thakir-Prayer-Times.desktop</launchable>
